plot: The group manages to return to Jersey in one piece and it is officially back to reality. Teresa models in a photo shoot for her upcoming book and Dolores takes her son Frankie on a college tour. Later, the kitchen isn't the only thing heating up as the Gorgas prepare for their restaurant opening when Teresa and Melissa go head-to-head over a business decision. Finally, Danielle receives some closure she has been wanting for over 9 years.
